---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageTitle: "Mechanics, Body Shops & Auto Services in Schuylkill County, PA"
description: "Find trusted mechanics, body shops, tire shops, and towing services in Schuylkill County, PA. A free community directory for Coal Region drivers."
---

<div class="container">
  <h1>Find Trusted Auto Shops in the Coal Region</h1>
  <p class="page-intro">
    Mechanics, body shops, tire shops, and towing services serving Schuylkill County. Every listing verified. No guesswork, no scrolling through national platforms that don't know Pottsville from Pittsburgh.
  </p>

  {% include "components/featured-listings.njk" %}

  <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);">
    {% for cat in businesses.categories %}
      <a href="/{{ cat.slug }}/" class="category-card">
        <span class="count">{{ cat.items.length }}</span>
        <span class="label">{{ cat.label }}</span>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Browse by City</h2>
    <div class="city-links">
      {% for city in businesses.cities %}
        {% if city.items.length >= 2 %}
          <a href="#{{ city.slug }}">{{ city.name }} ({{ city.items.length }})</a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Why Use This Directory?</h2>
    <p class="page-intro">
      National review sites bury small-town shops behind paid ads and SEO tricks. This directory lists every auto service provider in Schuylkill County — from the family shop on Route 61 to the tire center in Tamaqua. Real shops. Real phone numbers. No games.
    </p>
    <div class="city-links">
      <a href="/guides/how-to-find-honest-mechanic-schuylkill-county/">How to Find an Honest Mechanic</a>
      <a href="/guides/what-to-do-after-car-accident-pa/">What to Do After a Car Accident</a>
      <a href="/guides/seasonal-car-maintenance-coal-region/">Seasonal Car Maintenance</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebSite",
  "name": "{{ site.title }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}",
  "description": "{{ site.description }}"
}
</script>
